text:
Kylie Jenner/Instagram

Who says that having a child means the end of romance? Welcoming their daughter, Stormi, in February 2018 hasn't stopped new mom Kylie Jenner and boyfriend Travis Scott from enjoying their time together. The pair recently jet-setted to Europe for a trip that mixed both business and pleasure.

More from MamásLatinas: The lavish life of Kylie Jenner's baby, Stormi

According to E! News, the baby wasn't with them but the pair seemed to have a lovely time together. The rapper was scheduled to perform at various shows during their trip and his girl was right by his side supporting him. While neither of them shared photos to Instagram of their trip, they snapped some adorable behind the scenes look at their European rendezvous and shared them on Snapchat.

The usually private couple made a joint appearance on the cover of GQ's August issue, and it seems like they're becoming more comfortable with welcoming the world into their relationship. The Eurotrip hasn't been their first trip together but it's great seeing the new parents enjoy an adults-only trip.
